    "This comprehensive setup provides a robust platform for assessing the enhanced contextual understanding of Mistral LLM, demonstrating the efficacy and impact of integrating external knowledge bases into LLMs.",
    "ResultsThis section details the outcomes of the experiments conducted to assess the enhanced contextual understanding capabilities of Mistral LLM through the integration of external knowledge bases.",
    "Accuracy and Performance MetricsThe first area of evaluation focuses on quantitative metrics such as accuracy, precision, recall, and F1 score.",
    "The integration of external knowledge bases into Mistral LLM has resulted in substantial improvements across all these metrics when compared to its baseline version.",
